om\/en\/programs\/areas-of-intervention\/prevention-of-school-dropout\/\">Prevention of school dropout<\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/breakpoverty.com\/en\/programs\/areas-of-intervention\/access-to-first-employment\/\">Access to first employment<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>As a result of these three axes, more than 10 projects have been detected and are currently being financed and will benefit thousands of children. Your financial help as well as your commitment are vital components for the development of projects our foundation supports. It is also an extraordinary source of hope for the children and young adults who benefit from them.<\/p>\n<p>Join us and fight against poverty through a donation![\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\u00a0\u00bb\u00a0\u00bb row_type=\u00a0\u00bbrow\u00a0\u00bb use_row_as_full_screen_section=\u00a0\u00bbno\u00a0\u00bb type=\u00a0\u00bbgrid\u00a0\u00bb angled_section=\u00a0\u00bbno\u00a0\u00bb text_align=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb background_image_as_pattern=\u00a0\u00bbwithout_pattern\u00a0\u00bb background_color=\u00a0\u00bb#f8f8f8&Prime; padding_top=\u00a0\u00bb90&Prime; padding_bottom=\u00a0\u00bb90&Prime; z_index=\u00a0\u00bb\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime;][vc_single_image image=\u00a0\u00bb25511&Prime; img_size=\u00a0\u00bbfull\u00a0\u00bb alignment=\u00a0\u00bbcenter\u00a0\u00bb qode_css_animation=\u00a0\u00bbelement_from_left\u00a0\u00bb transition_delay=\u00a0\u00bb0.2&Prime;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=\u00a0\u00bb1\/2&Prime;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Making a donation<\/h2>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\u00a0\u00bbsmall\u00a0\u00bb position=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb color=\u00a0\u00bb#00a0e3&Prime; up=\u00a0\u00bb8&Prime; down=\u00a0\u00bb20&Prime;][vc_column_text css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1565079780047{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb]Making a donation against poverty is a way to actively participate in the fight against poverty and inequalities. Your donations allow the foundation to invest in innovative projects that are pioneers in reducing inequalities.<\/p>\n<p>The fight against extreme poverty is a collective battle. Therefore, we propose to contribute to each sum donated to the Break Poverty Foundation.[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1512745386048{padding-bottom: 10px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">1=2<\/h3>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1565079854360{padding-top: 15px !important;padding-bottom: 15px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\">Together, we will be stronger against poverty!<\/h6>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_separator type=\u00a0\u00bbtransparent\u00a0\u00bb up=\u00a0\u00bb5&Prime; down=\u00a0\u00bb16&Prime;][vc_row_inner row_type=\u00a0\u00bbrow\u00a0\u00bb type=\u00a0\u00bbfull_width\u00a0\u00bb text_align=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb css_animation=\u00a0\u00bb\u00a0\u00bb][vc_column_inner el_class=\u00a0\u00bbbutton_center\u00a0\u00bb]<a  itemprop=\"url\" href=\"https:\/\/don.breakpoverty.com\/b\/my-donation?\" target=\"_self\" data-hover-background-color='rgba(255,255,255,0.01)' data-hover-border-color='#cd2c5f' data-hover-color='#cd2c5f' class=\"qbutton  large center enlarge\" style=\"color: #ffffff; border-color: #cd2c5f; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; border-radius: 10px;-moz-border-radius: 10px;-webkit-border-radius: 10px; background-color: #cd2c5f;\">DONATE NOW<\/a>[\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\u00a0\u00bb\u00a0\u00bb row_type=\u00a0\u00bbrow\u00a0\u00bb use_row_as_full_screen_section=\u00a0\u00bbno\u00a0\u00bb type=\u00a0\u00bbgrid\u00a0\u00bb angled_section=\u00a0\u00bbno\u00a0\u00bb text_align=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb background_image_as_pattern=\u00a0\u00bbwithout_pattern\u00a0\u00bb z_index=\u00a0\u00bb\u00a0\u00bb css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1513244740308{marg